data.description: Location!!!! Lovely neighborhood. NO HOA's!! Perfect River Retreat home, sits on a Huge lot over 10,000 sqft!! Room for your RV and all of your Toys. This home features over 2000 sqft. Three bedrooms Two bathrooms, Master Suite, Spacious kitchen with a window view, convenient, breakfast bar, and formal dining space. The side slider leads to your backyard Oasis taking in the Mountainous Panoramic views. The Greatroom has an open concept feel, Office/Bonus room* Approximately 400 sqft. Attached is A car garage, Minutes from the Colorado River, a short drive to Lake Mohave, Laughlin Casinos Nightlife. Located close to shopping, restaurants, and medical facilities.Walking distance to Chaparral Golf Course.
